ng-new-yorks-empire-state-building-to-propose/articleshow/132140394.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/meet-angela-nikolau-and-ivan-kuznetsov-russian-couple-arrested-after-climbing-new-yorks-empire-state-building-to-propose/articleshow/132140394.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-02T20:24:41+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132141167,imgsize-134550.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Tax cuts, pension overhaul and sick leave reforms: Germany launches sweeping economic overhaul]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132140980.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Under Chancellor Friedrich Merz, the government has rolled out a transformative economic reform initiative intended to enhance Germany's financial landscape. The plan encompasses significant tax cuts for families, adjustments in the pension system that raise the retirement age, and new sick leave policies that require doctor’s notes from day one.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/tax-cuts-pension-overhaul-and-sick-leave-reforms-germany-launches-sweeping-economic-overhaul/articleshow/132140980.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/tax-cuts-pension-overhaul-and-sick-leave-reforms-germany-launches-sweeping-economic-overhaul/articleshow/132140980.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-02T20:10:43+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Business Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132140980,imgsize-212358.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['US spends $999bn, others much lower': Trump blasts Nato; how true is his claim?]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132140924.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-spends-999bn-others-much-lower-trump-blasts-nato-how-true-is-his-claim/articleshow/132140924.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-spends-999bn-others-much-lower-trump-blasts-nato-how-true-is-his-claim/articleshow/132140924.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-02T20:10:21+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132141003,imgsize-67251.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Rochdale grooming gang leader released as deportation loophole sparks fury across the UK]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132140576.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Rochdale grooming gang leader Shabir Ahmed's release after 14 years has sparked outrage as a legal loophole prevents his deportation despite serious sexual offence convictions.  Ahmed, stripped of citizenship, remains in the UK due to old immigration laws protecting pre-1973 Commonwealth settlers.  Victims and campaigners decry the justice system's failure, while strict licence conditions aim to protect the public.  The case intensifies calls for immigration law reform.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/rochdale-grooming-gang-leader-released-as-deportation-loophole-sparks-fury-across-the-uk/articleshow/132140576.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/rochdale-grooming-gang-leader-released-as-deportation-loophole-sparks-fury-across-the-uk/articleshow/132140576.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-02T19:59:46+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132140916,imgsize-60624.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Indian student denied entry to the US because of a WhatsApp group? A viral post asks international students to be alert]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132140365.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/indian-student-denied-entry-to-the-us-because-of-a-whatsapp-group-a-viral-post-asks-international-students-to-be-alert/articleshow/132140365.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/indian-student-denied-entry-to-the-us-because-of-a-whatsapp-group-a-viral-post-asks-international-students-to-be-alert/articleshow/132140365.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-02T19:19:45+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132140387,imgsize-231268.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Zohran Mamdani asks residents to 'set AC to 78 degrees'; MAGA says, 'This is socialism']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132123564.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/nyc-mayor-zohran-mamdani-asks-residents-to-set-ac-to-78-degrees-amid-heat-wave-maga-says-this-is-what-socialism-looks-like/articleshow/132123564.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/nyc-mayor-zohran-mamdani-asks-residents-to-set-ac-to-78-degrees-amid-heat-wave-maga-says-this-is-what-socialism-looks-like/articleshow/132123564.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-02T19:11:43+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:c